channel.title: What happened to Overloadx?
channel.description:
Now I'm not really active in RSPS communities, but what happened to the OverloadX source and client, I saw many reposts of the overloadx release with download links and mirrors but now when I went back to try download it I can't find a working link...
Does anyone have the OverloadX source and client? Or even a slightly modified version of it? I'd greatly appreciate a link - Thanks.

item.title: What happened to Overloadx?

item.description:
@Cruel_Truth wrote:

Yeah check on rune-server I also saw an old version somewhere over there.

Now if you are talking about the unreleased version that has been updated with epic agility and that type of stuff…I only know of like seven people with it.
